dBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:18:04.000Z","msg":"d小學雞寫既病毒太垃圾/特登放生你地先有得解密<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果server side gen個pki，得public key掉落電腦，對每個file gen aes key，逐個逐個buffer encrypt + inplace replace，臨尾append個rsa encrypt左既aes key落去，即係正常file加密方法<br />\n<br />\n你覺得會有解密程式咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:21:33.000Z","msg":"比贖金之後，server掉返個private key比你，可以係每個file既尾拎返rsa加密左既aes key，再用aes key decrypt返個file<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以連fbi都建議你比贖金<br />\n<br />\n(唔一定係rsa，可能係其他asym encryption，例如ecdsa或者ed25519，key size更細但一樣難解)"},{"pid":"da8aa08c5200e993fdaa4359cc2edf80738f6128","tid":797673,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6d80d8cedd344ed627a8c3775b02bbfd77ff6ab","tid":797673,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9775a741da87e758aeb1814aee3e30a5e5fffb97","tid":797673,"uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:13:36.000Z","msg":"成日見人中毒，就係唔用mac機或者linux"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.wixstatic.com/media/4da096_f9046fd255334ed19da63c7fa5286b31~mv2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2F4da096_f9046fd255334ed19da63c7fa5286b31~mv2.gif&h=ea423a06&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:22:00.000Z","msg":"d贖金夠你買部mac啦"},{"pid":"3b3a64fcb9eb6c33bd2c0e72471d98ee413acec4","tid":797673,"uid":192311,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T04:24:37.000Z","msg":"中毒？<br